# How AI Learns

AI is trained using two major approaches.

## 1. Massive Data Training

The model learns from huge amounts of text and data.

This is similar to how humans learn language through exposure.

## 2. Human Feedback (RLHF)

Humans review outputs and teach the AI:

- What is useful
- What is harmful
- What is safe

This process helps improve quality and behavior.

## Why This Matters

AI can still:

- Hallucinate facts
- Sound confident while being wrong
- Miss important context

### Practical Application

Never blindly trust outputs.

Always validate important information independently.

